OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FNearly 60,000 applications to the
OL,8,FBritish armed forces have been
OL,9,Frejected on medical grounds since July
OL,10,F2024, data has shown.
OL,12,FSome 45,680 applications to the
OL,13,FBritish Army were rejected between
OL,14,FJuly 2024 and January 2026, as well as
OL,15,F12,310 to the Royal Air Force and
OL,16,F1,020 to the navy, Ministry of Defence
OL,17,Ffigures show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
