FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FThe data was shared by the Ministry of
OL,8,FDefence minister Louise Sandher-Jones
OL,9,Fin a written parliamentary answer to a
OL,10,Fquestion asked by MP James Cartlidge
OL,11,Fon March 9.
OL,13,FThe numbers could include people who
OL,14,Fhave applied and been rejected more
OL,15,Fthan once, the minister said.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FMedical conditions that could impact
OL,8,Fentry to the British Army include
OL,9,Fchronic back pain, knee injuries,
OL,10,Fdeafness, migraines, widespread
OL,11,Fpsoriasis, diabetes, or hypertension,
OL,12,Faccording to its website.
OL,14,FBeing an organ transplant recipient,
OL,15,Fhaving a serious food allergy, or poor
OL,16,Fdental hygiene, including needing the
OL,17,Fremoval of teeth, could also cause an
OL,18,Fapplication to be rejected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FA decade-old rule banning people with
OL,8,Fasthma or severe acne was overturned
OL,9,Fin 2024 in a bid to boost recruitment.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the Labour Party
OL,12,Fconference the same year, defence
OL,13,Fsecretary John Healey said more than
OL,14,F100 regulations that stop "the
OL,15,Fbrightest and the best" from enlisting
OL,16,Fwould be removed.
OL,18,F"We will create an Armed Forces that
OL,19,Fdraws the very best of British talent.
OL,20,FBetter fit to fight. Better reflecting
OL,21,Fthe country they defend," Healey said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FAs well as failing medical checks,
OL,8,Fapplicants are most frequently
OL,9,Frejected for failing security
OL,10,Fclearance, not having the required
OL,11,Fresidency, not being fit enough, or
OL,12,Ffailing to get the right test scores
OL,13,Ffor their desired branch, according to
OL,14,Fa quarterly report from the MOD, last
OL,15,Fupdated in November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
