FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FIt said there were 155,520 people who
OL,8,Fapplied to join the British Army
OL,9,FRegular Forces between June 2024 and
OL,10,FJune 2025, and 51,290 people who
OL,11,Fapplied to join the RAF across the
OL,12,Fsame period.
OL,14,FITV News contacted the MOD for comment.
OL,16,FThe UK has so far refused to join the
OL,17,FUS and Israel in its offensive against
OL,18,FIran, but it has sent Typhoon fighter
OL,19,Fjets and Wildcat helicopters to
OL,20,F"strengthen defensive operations" in
OL,21,Fcountries like Cyprus and Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the UK warship HMS Dragon
OL,8,Fset off for Cyprus, after a British
OL,9,Fbase on the island was hit by an
OL,10,FIranian drone during the opening days
OL,11,Fof the war.
OL,13,FThe UK is also preparing to deploy the
OL,14,FRFA Lyme Bay, a Bay Class Landing
OL,15,FShip, in the Eastern Mediterranean,
OL,16,F"should she be needed to assist in
OL,17,Fmaritime tasks", the MOD said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
