FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773223748
OL,3,CAlmost 60,000 UK armed forces
OL,4,Capplications rejected on medical
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FThe ship is capable of offloading
OL,8,Ftroops and armoured vehicles to shore,
OL,9,Fand is "well-suited for humanitarian
OL,10,Fand disaster relief missions", a
OL,11,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
